{
  "stem": "27443.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rest of them, we didn't know where they were going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But later, we found out that they went to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did we hear about it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when we were marching into camp, the line that I was selected, we marched into camp, and we were marching in-- under the orders from kapos.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of the kapos were Germans, some of the kapos were Jews, with a band wearing on their arm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jews told us, you're lucky, because you were selected to live.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you're going to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were asking, what do you mean to live?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where are the other people?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't you know where you are?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is a death camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whoever is not in the line, do you see the chimneys?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Those are-- this is odor from flesh.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From human lives.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What did you think and feel?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We couldn't visualize.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a young girl, and I was really a child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And how was I-- how was I selected to go into the line to be alive?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really don't know to this day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I was a young girl, and I wasn't even really [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] pretty, I can't even say.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I didn't know at that time if I was a girl or a boy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I wasn't even [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] looking like a woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But I was taken into the line.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We marched into camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were going into showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were disrobed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were throwing to us clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Whatever-- whatever was thrown to you, you had to wear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were wearing certain clothes, and we were painted on our clothes, a big Kalel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It means [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Concentrations Lager ?].",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
